              "text": "Thanks."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "I'm not paying that!"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Roy",
              "text": "Then for now, our business is at an end."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "What happened to Carl?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Roy",
              "text": "Carl?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "The old barkeep."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Roy",
              "text": "Oh yes, Carl!"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Roy",
              "text": "He had to leave I'm afraid. Fear not though. I have taken over things here."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "And you are?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Roy",
              "text": "Roy is the name. Now, could I interest you in one of our finest Bloody Bracers?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "I'm not thirsty."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Roy",
              "text": "Then for now, our business is at an end."
            }
          ]
